TEXT.S: = Tjanavakung = Gaga mniq Pingtung Macyasyang ka alang Tjanavakung. 44 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 116 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 98% niqan 114 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 2% niqan 2 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Paiwan91%, Rukai3%, Tayal1%, ni rahuq na o3%.
